reviews.text: Great place for medium sized groups. We had roughly 20 people and their party room served us well. The lamb and meat platters were both grilled to perfection. The dips/hummus was nicely done as well.

Friendly staff in a nice environment! 
Located at end of escalator, easy to find! 
Explore the menu a la carte and travel to Greece .. good food for value!
Really good tasting Food. Price is good for it's taste. Service takes time though.

I had lunch there with a friend.
Ordered the grilled octopus , a Greek salad and the souvlaki .
Food was nIcely done , with generous portions.
We enjoyed the bright airy ambience of the restaurant .
Will definitely go back to try the other items on their menu
Nice food, nice environment and convenient.
